game

Class Player

  • java.lang.Object
    • game.internal.entities.GameObject
      • game.Player
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    CurrencyPlayer, EnemyPlayer

    public abstract class Player
extends GameObject
    Represents a player in the game. This class is to be subclassed and the cycle(Data, Shop) method be implemented. This class is designed such that a user can implement a custom subclass with access to certain methods and information, which is intended to be used to create artificial intelligence for the player.
    Version:
    1.0 - January 8th 2023
    Author:
    Tommy Shan and Harry Xu
